title: Taurus By Zenith E-Juice
description: Zenith E-Juice took America’s favorite cookie and turned it into the ultimate dessert-flavored vape. This flavor tastes exactly like an all-too-familiar chocolate cookie stuffed with velvety whipped cream. Each inhale of Taurus e-liquid envelops every taste bud in a decadent cookies and cream flavor. You’ll taste the sugary sweetness as the vapor absorbs into the tongue. When you exhale, a blend of your favorite sandwich cookie and fluffy whipped cream takes care of your sweet tooth’s cravings—all without needing to take a trip to the dentist.
